{"id":128035,"type":6,"name":"一路向南","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c4/3a/128035_Cuhgi.jpg","summary":"　　2009年，一部《搭车去柏林》见证了穿越中国、中亚和欧洲，直达德国柏林的艰辛浪漫的旅程。2010年9月，美籍青年谷岳（谷岳 Kyle Johnson）再次出发，只身搭上集装箱巨轮横渡太平洋，与纪录片导演刘畅（刘畅 Chang Liu）在阿拉斯加会合，开始了他们的美洲穿越计划。他们将从北极圈出发，以阿根廷最南端为目的地。三万三千公里的旅程，不同文化中的各种奇特职业。一位环球旅行者，一位纪录片导演，将用最小的低碳足迹完成世界上最长的陆地穿越。 \r\n　　纪录片同名著作《一路向南：到世界的边缘》也于2011年6月出版。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>一路向南</li><li><span>集数: </span>20</li><li><span>开始: </span>2010-12-20</li><li><span>类型: </span>纪录片</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>每集长: </span>22min</li><li><span>导演: </span>谷岳 / 刘畅</li><li><span>主演: </span>谷岳 / 刘畅</li>","eps":[{"id":500013,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500013","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500014,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500014","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500015,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500015","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500016,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500016","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500017,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500017","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500018,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500018","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500019,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500019","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500020,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500020","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":500021,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/500021","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}